main event: A military radar observation tracked 25 unidentified flying objects over Goose AFB in Labrador on June 13, 1955.
interesting points: The sighting was established by multiple radar operators,The objects were tracked for approximately 2 minutes and 15 seconds,No photos or physical evidence were reported,The radar contact indicated a significant number of objects within a short observation period,This incident adds to the historical data collected by Project Blue Book.
